Module CAViewer
Package sample.model

Class Simulator

java.lang.Object
sample.model.Grid
sample.model.Simulator
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Iterable<Coordinate>, java.util.Iterator<Coordinate>
Direct Known Subclasses:
Pattern
public class Simulator
extends Grid
Simulations are run using Simulator.

Example Usage: 
 Simulator simulator = new Simulator(new HROT("B3/S23"));
 simulator.fromRLE("bo$obo$o2bo$bobo$2bo!", new Coordinate(0, 0));
 simulator.step();
 for (Coordinate cell: simulator) {
      System.out.println(cell);
 }
